  "id": "e849391b-83e0-5fe1-b7c9-47dbbaddd9ee",
  "slug": "how-to-make-black-forest-cupcake",
  "name": "Black Forest Cupcake Recipe",
  "recipe_type": "dessert",
  "brief_description": "This Black Forest Cupcake Recipe will surely capture your sweet tooth. Try this by following our step by step procedure.",
  "cuisine": null,
  "instructions": [
    {
      "position": 1,
      "text": "Preheat oven to 350 degrees Fahrenheit"
    },
    {
      "position": 2,
      "text": "Combine flour, salt, cocoa powder, baking soda in a mixing bowl then whisk using a balloon whisk. This will be our dry ingredient mixture."
    },
    {
      "position": 3,
      "text": "Place the softened butter on a clean mixing bowl then cream using an electric hand or stand mixer. Gradually add the sugar while creaming."
    },
    {
      "position": 4,
      "text": "Put-in the vanilla extract and gradually whisk-in the eggs."
    },
    {
      "position": 5,
      "text": "Alternately whisk in the dry ingredient mixture and buttermilk then continue mixing until well blended."
    },
    {
      "position": 6,
      "text": "Arrange paper cups on your cupcake pans then pour-in the mixture in each cup. Do not completely fill the cups. Leave a space for expansion."
    },
    {
      "position": 7,
      "text": "Place in the oven and bake for 20 minutes."
    },
    {
      "position": 8,
      "text": "Remove from the oven and let cool."
    },
    {
      "position": 9,
      "text": "Meanwhile, make the filling by combining the filling ingredients in a bowl. Mix well."
    },
    {
      "position": 10,
      "text": "Make a space in the middle of the cupcake by scraping it or inserting a hollow tube, then put a teaspoon or two of the filling."
    },
    {
      "position": 11,
      "text": "Make the frosting by placing the heavy whipping cream in a bowl then whisk using an electric hand or stand mixer. Gradually mix-in the confectioners (powder) sugar and continue mixing until soft peaks form. Turn off the mixer and add the vanilla extract and fold."
    },
    {
      "position": 12,
      "text": "Frost the cupcakes using the frosting."
    },
    {
      "position": 13,
      "text": "Garnish with chocolate shavings (like what we had with the No-bake Chocolate fudge tart) and a fresh cherry on top."
    },
    {
      "position": 14,
      "text": "Serve right away or refrigerate before serving."
    },
    {
      "position": 15,
      "text": "Share and enjoy!"
    }
  ],
  "servings": 6,
